{"tid":1550351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推自殺POST前 請三思","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:33.000Z","uid":64092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9dd954fe85429b517d49fbb3193bbb54fa2e7d3","tid":1550351,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[又有屍體]blablabla</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n共產黨又殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死黑警又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂你估你真係神探咩 而家當連登係香討定BK呀<br />\n推負面POST不特止仲要係到散播恐慌<br />\n<br />\n知唔知<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自殺係會傳染</strong></span>架 而家成個社會氣氛咁低迷<br />\n正常人見到依啲新聞都唔好受啦 你地<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有無諗過香港幾多人有情緒問題</strong></span>呀<br />\n依啲嘩眾取寵嘅標題同不負責任嘅留言分分鐘就係佢地嘅導火線呀"},{"pid":"9ad878f69ebf696c60d4da391f6f36aff2439c1f","tid":1550351,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77b77d3e61dd31a94168bdf32518335a250a0318","tid":1550351,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=a0e4d300\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"c45efed7c075c9b17eaa7291fe869ff966ed2745","tid":1550351,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>2019年香港自殺資料統計</ins></strong><br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=1cc3e4b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=bfefe4af\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=f1fc7eba\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>"}]}